This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) as it deals with textual claim verification and introduces a new dataset for fact extraction and verification. It also involves the use of machine learning algorithms and models for classification, which falls under the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Information Retrieval (cs.IR) is also a possible sub-category as the paper involves the retrieval of evidence to support or refute a claim. Finally, Cybersecurity and Privacy (cs.CY) is a less likely sub-category as it is not directly related to the topic of the paper, but it may be relevant in the context of verifying claims related to cybersecurity and privacy.
